Provides: heroic-games-launcher
Description: Open source launcher for Epic, Amazon and GOG Games
 Heroic is an open-source game launcher for Linux, Windows and macOS.
 It supports launching games from Epic Games Store, GOG.com, and
 Amazon Prime Gaming.
 .
 Features include:
  * Native game installation and management
  * Wine/Proton manager for compatibility layers
  * Integration with MangoHUD, GameMode, and ProtonUp-Qt
  * Cloud saves synchronization
  * Built-in browser for store pages
 .
 This package repackages the official upstream .deb for Debian Unstable.
